entries.hail: How are you?  Don't you just love this shirt?
entries.lunatic: I'm just a fashion conscious Wookiee.  Why don't you go talk to that bothan girl over there?  She may have something for you to do.
entries.ooh: I hear you've got a jacket I might be interested in.  I'd take it, but it's really the Calamari's.
entries.take: Why don't you just take it?
entries.know: I know.  But perhaps she doesn't want it.  If not, bring it back to me, please!
entries.cant: I couldn't do that in good conscience.  I know it's someone else's jacket.
entries.goody: Rumor has it you're going to offer me that jacket I want.
entries.cash: Not so fast....what do I get?
entries.money: Here.  Here's a deed to a moisture vaporator.  Now let me have that jacket!  <YOINK!>
entries.nothing: You don't even have the jacket anymore!
